9 Pictures of Beautiful Canada 🇨🇦 Wanna see your pictures posted in our account? Apply for a feature on worlderlust.com (link in my bio: @worlderlust)

node.text:
The tallest Waterfall In North America, Upper Yosemite Falls! 💦 Wanna see your pictures posted in our account? Apply for a feature on worlderlust.com (link in my bio: @worlderlust)

This is the view from the upper Yosemite Falls trail after the first set of switchbacks. Can you believe that this is only the upper portion of the falls? There is a middle portion AND a lower part of the falls as well!

📽 @thedomesticgypsy_
📍Upper Yosemite Falls, California
🎶 Labrinth•Still Don't Know My Name

node.text:
Would you dare to walk on this Via Ferrata? 😳 Get your photos posted in our account, apply for a feature visiting worlderlust.com 👉🏼 the link is in our bio: @worlderlust

The new Ferrata Delle Aquile, on the top of Paganella, is a highly emotional and spectacular via ferrata that gives you unforgettable emotions; the sight embraces whole Trentino, but keeping fixed on the track too.

Recommendation:
Avoid the queue: purchase online your ticket and go directly to turnstile. Choose the stage and pay with your credit card. You will receive by email your ticket (you can print the ticket or save it in your smartphone), scan it on the orange scanner on the turnstile located at the gates of the lift.

📽 @niklaskoessel
📍Trentino, Italy
